text: Hans Schmid (born 24 June 1948) is a Swiss ski jumper. He competed at the 1972 Winter Olympics and the 1976 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1972 Winter Olympics Category:Ski jumpers at the 1976 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
